{"id":14881764,"mediaExerciseId":"e894b63d-5e0c-443f-868a-1c3806bca4d1","exerciseName":"6","chapterName":"21","chapterTitle":"International Corporate Finance","groupId":612470,"groupTitle":"Critical Thinking Questions","isPremium":true,"sectionName":null,"sectionTitle":null,"pageNumber":735,"solutions":[{"id":5978829,"modifiedOn":"2021-01-01T00:00:00.000000","steps":[{"columns":[{"text":"In this exercise, we are asked to analyze the situation regarding international risks.","images":{"latex":{"large":{"height":61,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/03/acef0f79e33c909b4a238ef63e0aab35/f3ddf74c2db73c32d71bbe9495161cbd/lateximg_large.png","width":996},"regular":{"height":32,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/03/acef0f79e33c909b4a238ef63e0aab35/f3ddf74c2db73c32d71bbe9495161cbd/lateximg.png","width":498}},"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":true}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":1},{"columns":[{"text":"Duracell International was planning to open battery-manufacturing plants in China and India. It will give an advantage to the company since it avoid import duties of between 30 and 35 percent that have made alkaline batteries prohibitively expensive for some consumers.","images":{"latex":{"large":{"height":141,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/03/acef0f79e33c909b4a238ef63e0aab35/55ed4b6602c7f3d625d0207420b2e665/lateximg_large.png","width":996},"regular":{"height":72,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/03/acef0f79e33c909b4a238ef63e0aab35/55ed4b6602c7f3d625d0207420b2e665/lateximg.png","width":498}},"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":true}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":2},{"columns":[{"text":"Another advantage of planning to open branches in China and India is the **reduce expenses**. Now that Duracell will have plants in China and India, the expenses such as transportation and taxes will decrease since they have plants in the following countries already.","images":{"latex":{"large":{"height":141,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/03/acef0f79e33c909b4a238ef63e0aab35/9b9267b5a23c702fe77ae2d6cca13c39/lateximg_large.png","width":997},"regular":{"height":72,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/03/acef0f79e33c909b4a238ef63e0aab35/9b9267b5a23c702fe77ae2d6cca13c39/lateximg.png","width":498}},"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":false}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":3},{"columns":[{"text":"Moreover, it will **reduced the exchange rate risk** . Exchange rate risk is a risk that happens during international operations because of the changes in currency values. Therefore, managing this risk is important in the international finance. Duracell managed the exchange rate risk by setting up power plants in China and India.","images":{"latex":{"large":{"height":176,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/03/acef0f79e33c909b4a238ef63e0aab35/cef9797e5f475ee66aa38fa1d8ce408b/lateximg_large.png","width":1027},"regular":{"height":89,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/03/acef0f79e33c909b4a238ef63e0aab35/cef9797e5f475ee66aa38fa1d8ce408b/lateximg.png","width":514}},"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":false}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":4},{"columns":[{"text":"Along with the additional advantages, additional risks will also apply. One of it is the **political risk**. A political risk is a risk related to changes in value because of political actions. Some countries have a higher political risk than others. The higher the political risk, the higher required return on overseas investments. Moreover, political risk also depends on the nature of the business since the more valuable the business is, the higher its political risk.","images":{"latex":{"large":{"height":249,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/03/acef0f79e33c909b4a238ef63e0aab35/72295cf42ed43ddf5b7bab1c4653e1a5/lateximg_large.png","width":998},"regular":{"height":126,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/03/acef0f79e33c909b4a238ef63e0aab35/72295cf42ed43ddf5b7bab1c4653e1a5/lateximg.png","width":500}},"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":false}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":5},{"columns":[{"text":"Hence, Duracell must take note of the political aspects of China and India to manage the political risk and structure it as a branch so that the parent company will be more involved.","images":{"latex":{"large":{"height":103,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/03/acef0f79e33c909b4a238ef63e0aab35/97e3c75393b3617e7a607a7650bd9a13/lateximg_large.png","width":997},"regular":{"height":53,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/03/acef0f79e33c909b4a238ef63e0aab35/97e3c75393b3617e7a607a7650bd9a13/lateximg.png","width":497}},"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":true}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":6},{"columns":[{"text":"Another risk is that it will **increase expenses**. Although the expenses will decrease such as the transactions and taxes, additional expenses will also incur such as the salaries and utilities for the new plants. ","images":{"latex":{"large":{"height":105,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/03/acef0f79e33c909b4a238ef63e0aab35/48c56af2310e4233db26fcb0bb9ca689/lateximg_large.png","width":996},"regular":{"height":53,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/03/acef0f79e33c909b4a238ef63e0aab35/48c56af2310e4233db26fcb0bb9ca689/lateximg.png","width":498}},"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":false}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":7},{"columns":[{"text":"As a conclusion, the advantages of having a branch in China and India will decrease expenses such as transportation and taxes and the exchange rate risk will be properly managed.\n\\\nOn the other hand, the disadvantage of having a branch in China and India will increase expenses such as salaries and utilities and increase the political risk.","images":{"latex":{"large":{"height":179,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/03/acef0f79e33c909b4a238ef63e0aab35/09509f79aaae480be63da1b8d46cb432/lateximg_large.png","width":998},"regular":{"height":91,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/03/acef0f79e33c909b4a238ef63e0aab35/09509f79aaae480be63da1b8d46cb432/lateximg.png","width":500}},"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":false}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":8}],"rating":5,"solutionUuid":"92d92fa9-62a5-43a5-913d-cf87407d0c6b","editorVersion":2,"answeredOn":null,"ratingCount":null,"solutionOrder":null,"totalSteps":8}],"textbook":{"authors":"Bradford D. Jordan, Randolph W. Westerfield, Stephen A. Ross","imageUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/textbook_covers/tmpm0p82b7h","imageThumbnailUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/cache/d1/d3/d1d34d106dd29dd2e71be582412ef59d.jpg","id":34320,"isbn":"9781259918957","isPremium":true,"title":"Fundamentals of Corporate Finance","edition":"12th Edition","verifiedSolutionCount":1217,"shouldBeIndexableForSeo":true,"modified":1665448474394,"active":true,"publisher":"McGraw-Hill Education","mainTextbookIsbn":null,"subjects":{"level1":["Social Science"],"level2":["Economics"],"level3":["Finance"]}},"nextExercises":[{"id":14881765,"exerciseName":"7","page":735,"hasSolution":true,"mediaExerciseId":"12da99fd-3193-4d85-bcb1-7b43be9dc139","_webUrl":"https://quizlet.com/explanations/textbook-solutions/fundamentals-of-corporate-finance-12th-edition-9781259918957/chapter-21-critical-thinking-questions-7-12da99fd-3193-4d85-bcb1-7b43be9dc139"},{"id":14881766,"exerciseName":"8","page":735,"hasSolution":true,"mediaExerciseId":"fcb0e8a4-9595-4bc7-90a5-a5538f4dbf16","_webUrl":"https://quizlet.com/explanations/textbook-solutions/fundamentals-of-corporate-finance-12th-edition-9781259918957/chapter-21-critical-thinking-questions-8-fcb0e8a4-9595-4bc7-90a5-a5538f4dbf16"}],"previousExercises":[{"id":14881763,"exerciseName":"5","page":735,"hasSo